1
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:03,325
Yuho isn't at his best today.

2
00:00:03,325 --> 00:00:06,039
Sungwoo must be tired too.

3
00:00:06,040 --> 00:00:07,470
I'm fine.

4
00:00:07,470 --> 00:00:10,400
♫ <i> Approaching is prohibited </i> ♫

5
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:14,060
<i> [The Witch Store]</i>

6
00:00:14,060 --> 00:00:17,590
<i> [Episode 5] 
 [Things You Want to Hide From Your Crush]</i>

7
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:27,980
<i> Flip over!</i>

8
00:00:31,380 --> 00:00:32,940
1:30 pm? I'm late!

9
00:00:32,940 --> 00:00:36,540
You can be a golden medalist.

10
00:00:59,140 --> 00:01:00,676
Should I tell you who wins?

11
00:01:00,676 --> 00:01:02,440
Don't spoil it.

12
00:01:02,440 --> 00:01:05,759
- Sungwoo... 
 - Don't.

13
00:01:05,759 --> 00:01:07,696
Wow, awesome!

14
00:01:07,696 --> 00:01:10,400
Yoon Sungwoo is amazing.

15
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,780
Oh, yeah.

16
00:01:11,780 --> 00:01:13,500
Flip him over!

17
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:15,080
Grab the collar.

18
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,660
Stop.

19
00:01:26,980 --> 00:01:29,460
Wow, you did it.

20
00:01:31,540 --> 00:01:32,980
Sungwoo!

21
00:01:32,980 --> 00:01:36,260
Wow, he is too good.

22
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:45,080
Wow, awesome! He is the best!

23
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:47,740
Yoon Sungwoo is really awesome.

24
00:01:47,740 --> 00:01:49,360
It is fun.

25
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:51,900
He is really cool.

26
00:01:51,900 --> 00:01:54,300
I think I can do it.

27
00:01:55,300 --> 00:01:57,996
- Hey. 
 - Hey! Good job.

28
00:01:57,996 --> 00:01:59,436
- Good job. Good. 
 - You did a good job.

29
00:01:59,436 --> 00:02:01,520
- Good job today! 
 - Yoon Sungwoo.

30
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:04,400
Wow, you beat up all of them.

31
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,840
- You're the best. 
 - You did a really good job.

32
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:09,279
Well, thank you for coming to see me.

33
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:11,316
Let's go. I will treat you all.

34
00:02:11,316 --> 00:02:14,000
- Now? 
 - Yes, right now.

35
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,960
I am done with practice matches today.

36
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:18,336
Don't you have a match with Yuho today?

37
00:02:18,336 --> 00:02:19,416
With me?

38
00:02:19,416 --> 00:02:20,879
- With Yuho? 
 - Yeah.

39
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:24,260
Taeil said that he used to do judo.

40
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:27,460
He said that they would have a match.

41
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:29,540
Is that not happening today?

42
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:32,040
Well...

43
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:35,219
Yuho isn't at his best today.

44
00:02:35,220 --> 00:02:37,920
Sungwoo must be tired too.

45
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:40,000
I'm fine.

46
00:02:41,420 --> 00:02:43,660
I am... fine, too.

47
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:46,560
Oh, really? Why don't we give it a try?

48
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,900
Okay.

49
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:52,120
Wait. I will bring a wrist belt and a suit for you.

50
00:02:54,660 --> 00:02:56,920
Hey, what's wrong?

51
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:59,096
Why did you do that?

52
00:02:59,096 --> 00:03:01,776
- Do you want to make a bet? 
 - What bet?

53
00:03:01,776 --> 00:03:05,140
Let's see if Yuho will use the thing that I gave him.

54
00:03:05,140 --> 00:03:06,280
I bet that he'll use it.

55
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,180
He won't.

56
00:03:08,180 --> 00:03:10,100
Well...

57
00:03:12,260 --> 00:03:14,280
<i> Do I have to use it?</i>

58
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:18,480
<i> Okay, if that helps me win.</i>

59
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:33,460
♫ <i> I don't really know my heart </i> ♫

60
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:37,230
♫ <i> A dozen times a day </i> ♫

61
00:03:37,230 --> 00:03:41,450
♫ <i> It moves in your direction </i> ♫

62
00:03:41,450 --> 00:03:45,040
♫ <i> I don't know where my heart will go </i> ♫

63
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:47,560
Oh, Yuho is not that bad.

64
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:50,880
Wow, that thing is effective today.

65
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:53,220
That's not the one I gave him.

66
00:03:54,230 --> 00:03:57,480
♫ <i> Like the sound of a bell in my head </i> ♫

67
00:03:57,480 --> 00:04:02,010
♫ <i> I understood what it was </i> ♫

68
00:04:02,010 --> 00:04:09,740
♫ <i> I can feel you coming tonight if you recognize me </i> ♫

69
00:04:09,740 --> 00:04:18,410
♫ <i> 'Cuz far away, so lonely night would throw me towards you </i> ♫

70
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:35,620
Thank you, Sungwoo.

71
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:37,976
"Bon appetit!" If you want more, tell me.

72
00:04:37,976 --> 00:04:40,940
I am picky, so I can't eat much.

73
00:04:43,260 --> 00:04:44,900
Are you okay?

74
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,640
What?

75
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:49,620
Oh, thanks.

76
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:53,036
When did you start learning judo?

77
00:04:53,036 --> 00:04:55,216
- You were so good. 
 - Yeah.

78
00:04:55,216 --> 00:04:59,220
Yuho has a good physique so he's good at playing sports.

79
00:04:59,220 --> 00:05:00,580
Stop it.

80
00:05:00,580 --> 00:05:02,696
Yeah. You were cool.

81
00:05:02,696 --> 00:05:04,280
You were amazing.

82
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:07,420
Yes, you did a good job.

83
00:05:07,420 --> 00:05:09,020
- Sungwoo. 
 - Yeah.

84
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:10,540
I want more of it.

85
00:05:10,540 --> 00:05:12,876
Oh, order more if you want.

86
00:05:12,876 --> 00:05:15,339
Hey, finish the leftovers first before you order more.

87
00:05:15,340 --> 00:05:17,340
Are you the one paying? He said he would pay.

88
00:05:17,340 --> 00:05:18,920
Order more.

89
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:21,836
Please give us three more rice balls.

90
00:05:21,836 --> 00:05:26,000
Hey, we need five!

91
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,710
Get more if you want.

92
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:30,060
You don't eat?

93
00:05:30,780 --> 00:05:32,640
Go ahead.

94
00:05:33,420 --> 00:05:34,580
You don't?

95
00:05:34,580 --> 00:05:36,380
What? Oh?

96
00:05:36,380 --> 00:05:38,300
- This one. Green onions. 
 - Green onions?

97
00:05:38,300 --> 00:05:40,440
It is the best thing in here.

98
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,900
Oh, I am really full.

99
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:46,760
Well, I wish I could eat more.

100
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:49,696
Yeah, you only had a seven people portion by yourself.

101
00:05:49,696 --> 00:05:52,880
Oh, did I?

102
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:55,200
That place was so good.

103
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,980
I am happy for you.

104
00:05:56,980 --> 00:05:58,720
Hyeji, was it fine for you?

105
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:01,180
Yes, it was good.

106
00:06:01,180 --> 00:06:02,920
Hey, Hyeji.

107
00:06:04,260 --> 00:06:05,980
Well...

108
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:08,840
Hey, didn't you say that you were going to a bookstore?

109
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,900
- Me? 
 - Yes, you did.

110
00:06:10,900 --> 00:06:13,140
- Let's go. 
 - Why would I go to a bookstore?

111
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:14,780
Yeah, you must have misheard.

112
00:06:14,780 --> 00:06:16,416
He's never been to a bookstore.

113
00:06:16,416 --> 00:06:18,400
Right.

114
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,280
You'll go to the bookstore, right?

115
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,920
Yeah, I should go.

116
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:27,736
It is cold outside so I want to listen to a warm story.

117
00:06:27,736 --> 00:06:29,320
What?

118
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:32,376
Okay, we are leaving. See you on Monday.

119
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:34,356
- Oh, yeah. 
 - Bye.

120
00:06:34,356 --> 00:06:35,860
Let's go.

121
00:06:36,780 --> 00:06:41,190
Books are food for the soul.

122
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:42,990
♫ <i> How should I say it? </i> ♫

123
00:06:42,990 --> 00:06:46,060
What's wrong with him?

124
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:48,280
Thank you for walking me home.

125
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,720
I should get going.

126
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,136
Bye, Hyeji.

127
00:06:51,136 --> 00:06:52,980
Wait, Hyeji.

128
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,216
What are you doing tomorrow?

129
00:06:55,216 --> 00:06:58,560
Tomorrow? I don't have any plans.

130
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,520
Then, would you meet me tomorrow?

131
00:07:02,580 --> 00:07:04,980
Oh, I should get going.

132
00:07:04,980 --> 00:07:06,999
Oh, yeah. Bye, Yuho.

133
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,760
Take care.

134
00:07:09,380 --> 00:07:11,040
Do you have time?

135
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,579
Well, yeah.

136
00:07:12,580 --> 00:07:15,236
Okay, meet me in front of the station.

137
00:07:15,236 --> 00:07:16,336
See you.

138
00:07:16,336 --> 00:07:18,770
- Yeah, okay, bye! 
 - Bye!

139
00:07:24,380 --> 00:07:26,840
Today's fortune.

140
00:07:27,860 --> 00:07:29,580
Not good.

141
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:35,380
Why are you here? I told you to bring your friend here.

142
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:39,540
I am here to give it back to you.

143
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:43,336
You don't have to.

144
00:07:43,336 --> 00:07:44,699
I won't do judo anymore.

145
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:46,640
Well, it really worked.

146
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:50,439
- Of course it did, it was made by a witch. 
 - A witch?

147
00:07:50,439 --> 00:07:54,640
By the way, why didn't you use it since you knew it worked?

148
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:57,720
Well, using it wouldn't be fair.

149
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:59,860
Well, our part-timer is good at picking out good people.

150
00:07:59,860 --> 00:08:01,200
What?

151
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:04,180
Nothing. I was just talking to myself.

152
00:08:04,180 --> 00:08:06,000
Okay, then see you.

153
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,420
Okay.

154
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:10,100
Bring your friends here.

155
00:08:10,100 --> 00:08:12,140
Two.

156
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:15,880
<i>[Skin Lotion for Young Baby Faces]</i>

157
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:19,890
♫ <i> Like the sound of a bell in my head </i> ♫

158
00:08:19,890 --> 00:08:24,430
♫ <i> I understood what it was </i> ♫

159
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:26,920
♫ <i> I can feel you coming tonight if you recognize me </i> ♫

160
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:29,290
Should I have used it?

161
00:08:44,420 --> 00:08:48,040
Why did he want to meet with her tomorrow?
